<i>you'll still be in my heart...</i>

242
00:25:29,544 --> 00:25:34,072
<i>Sun and moon are coming in a path...</i>

243
00:25:34,616 --> 00:25:39,315
<i>Truth and vows have gone to the wind...</i>

244
00:25:40,055 --> 00:25:45,254
<i>l lost my life seeing</i>
<i>those shivering lips...</i>

245
00:25:47,162 --> 00:25:50,097
<i>Your beau is yearning</i>
<i>and seeking you...</i>

246
00:25:50,298 --> 00:25:52,596
<i>Give me your heart, my dear...</i>

247
00:25:52,968 --> 00:25:57,928
<i>Though you're beyond my reach,</i>
<i>my fingers wish to touch you...</i>

248
00:25:58,139 --> 00:26:03,372
<i>Though l know you're a ball of fire,</i>
<i>l want to play with it...</i>

249
00:26:48,023 --> 00:26:56,658
Here's come our leader!
- Bless me. - Bless you son.

250
00:26:57,032 --> 00:26:59,398
Greetings.
- Go...go...

251
00:27:05,707 --> 00:27:08,505
Now l know why didn't shoot her.

252
00:27:10,211 --> 00:27:11,576
l was foolish not to realise it.

253
00:27:12,213 --> 00:27:14,010
With one bullet it would be over,

254
00:27:14,549 --> 00:27:17,677
either me or he would've
gone to jail for few years.

255
00:27:18,053 --> 00:27:19,077
the problem would've been over.

256
00:27:19,654 --> 00:27:21,781
You too would've left her
thinking about future.

257
00:27:24,325 --> 00:27:25,417
Why do you think l left her?

258
00:27:25,727 --> 00:27:32,030
For 14 hours torture, SP has come
with 5 truck loads of police men.

259
00:27:33,068 --> 00:27:37,368
lf we keep him on toes for 14 days,
your idea is great.

260
00:27:39,541 --> 00:27:42,635
l was pointing a pistol at her,
a minute or two she would've died,

261
00:27:44,412 --> 00:27:45,470
she was standing fearless
like a dead body.

262
00:27:45,680 --> 00:27:47,307
Not a faint of fear, brother.

263
00:27:50,585 --> 00:27:52,382
How can l kill a fearless woman?

264
00:27:55,857 --> 00:28:01,056
Brother, would you've pulled the
trigger if you were in my place?

265
00:28:04,632 --> 00:28:06,657
l can't think so much.

266
00:28:07,268 --> 00:28:08,565
You want me to cut a goat
and prepare a soup.

267
00:28:08,770 --> 00:28:10,237
lt'll rock you.

268
00:28:11,172 --> 00:28:15,575
lf any boys here misbehave,
l can thrash or send them to jail,

269
00:28:15,777 --> 00:28:17,244
tell me, l'll do it in minutes.

270
00:28:18,513 --> 00:28:22,244
Women, fear are beyond me, brother.

271
00:28:34,395 --> 00:28:36,590
She's the new sister.

272
00:28:37,132 --> 00:28:41,364
What are you looking at?
Clear out.

273
00:28:44,139 --> 00:28:47,540
You won't get clothes here,
l found a leaf of my size,

274
00:28:47,742 --> 00:28:51,109
stitches it and
drape yourself in it.

275
00:28:51,312 --> 00:28:55,271
Uncle...
- Clear out kids!

276
00:28:58,653 --> 00:29:01,520
You won't laugh for a joke,
don't fear at a pointed gun,

277
00:29:01,856 --> 00:29:03,448
what sort of a life is it?

278
00:29:04,492 --> 00:29:07,120
Food!
Will you atleast respect this?

279
00:29:11,666 --> 00:29:15,295
Throw into the dustbin.
Am l a dog?

280
00:29:16,237 --> 00:29:18,296
To tie and feed me.

281
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:21,465
We are struggling for
generations for a meal only.

282
00:29:21,676 --> 00:29:24,304
So proud? Arrogance of rich.

283
00:29:24,512 --> 00:29:26,537
ls what you're doing good?

284
00:29:26,915 --> 00:29:29,315
Women are women.

285
00:29:29,517 --> 00:29:34,147
Feeling pity at your plight,
are you arguing with me?

286
00:29:34,355 --> 00:29:36,653
Look, my wife too never
shouted at me.

287
00:29:37,926 --> 00:29:41,657
Eat it or if you think
we are enemies, leave it.

288
00:29:42,530 --> 00:29:43,497
As you wish.

289
00:29:51,272 --> 00:29:54,764
ls salt okay?
Be loyal to us all your life.

290
00:29:55,710 --> 00:29:57,507
For my size.

291
00:30:56,871 --> 00:30:57,735
That's a pistol.

292
00:30:59,540 --> 00:31:00,905
Yes, it's a gun.

293
00:31:02,010 --> 00:31:03,568
Guiding us to their hideout.

294
00:31:27,669 --> 00:31:28,931
You talk to them sir.

295
00:32:41,542 --> 00:32:42,566
Where is Veeraiah?

296
00:32:43,544 --> 00:32:44,568
Where is Veeraiah?

297
00:32:46,647 --> 00:32:47,671
Where is Veeraiah?

298
00:33:37,031 --> 00:33:40,797
Veeraiah is a great man.
He never speaks loudly, sir.

299
00:33:41,436 --> 00:33:45,065
What's that language?
Great man? Crook, you're wrong, go.

300
00:33:47,175 --> 00:33:51,578
He's brave as his name,
he fights like a real warrior.

301
00:33:52,046 --> 00:33:54,173
He hacks anyone.

302
00:33:55,049 --> 00:33:58,416
These men don't know anything,
he's very kind hearted man,

303
00:33:58,686 --> 00:34:00,415
he's lovable than a mother,

304
00:34:00,621 --> 00:34:03,146
he's straightforward and
so gets into trouble easily.

305
00:34:03,624 --> 00:34:05,148
With outsiders too, like with us.

306
00:34:07,795 --> 00:34:11,856
He's a poet, he says anything
in shortest terms.

307
00:34:12,633 --> 00:34:13,600
ls he Thiruvalluvar?

308
00:34:13,801 --> 00:34:17,168
Girls swoon over him, sir.

309
00:34:19,740 --> 00:34:21,537
Not for all girls, go now.

310
00:34:22,810 --> 00:34:27,110
Not praising him too much,
but he's great in any role,

311
00:34:27,648 --> 00:34:29,946
very good drama actor.
Folk artiste too.

312
00:34:30,151 --> 00:34:33,848
When starts talking,
he'll make you laugh to tears.

313
00:34:34,155 --> 00:34:35,884
Your intestines will burn, go away.

314
00:34:36,090 --> 00:34:37,614
Very dangerous man, sir.

315
00:34:38,092 --> 00:34:43,621
A goon, a loafer, hacking people,
womanizer, he does everything.

316
00:34:44,932 --> 00:34:46,866
When he starts playing drums...

317
00:34:52,006 --> 00:34:55,533
He's God of Death in flesh.
Death is inevitable, sir.

318
00:34:55,743 --> 00:34:59,645
Enough of it, ten people have told
ten different things and confused us.

319
00:34:59,847 --> 00:35:01,075
l'm feeling giddy.

320
00:36:11,986 --> 00:36:15,717
ls it hand? Very hard.
Tough.

321
00:36:17,592 --> 00:36:20,720
Matched horoscopes
and 7 compatibilities,

322
00:36:21,596 --> 00:36:23,962
but failed to check if hands
and legs are soft.

323
00:36:24,365 --> 00:36:25,332
Your mother-in-law.

324
00:36:27,034 --> 00:36:30,834
My dear dancer,
this is a policeman's hand.

325
00:36:31,839 --> 00:36:32,828
Roguish hands.

326
00:36:34,008 --> 00:36:38,138
ls it fired or non-fired hands?

327
00:36:38,746 --> 00:36:39,804
Touch heart and say.

328
00:36:40,681 --> 00:36:43,912
l'll tell my dear.
- Go away.

329
00:36:49,890 --> 00:37:04,100
<i>Oh thief who barged into my eyes...</i>

330
00:37:04,305 --> 00:37:08,765
<i>Will you see with your hands?</i>

331
00:37:08,976 --> 00:37:13,777
<i>Will you join me with your eyes...</i>

332
00:37:13,981 --> 00:37:18,782
<i>Will you teach me your art?</i>

333
00:37:20,154 --> 00:37:24,784
<i>Our silent eyes won't sleep</i>
<i>thinking about me...</i>

334
00:37:24,992 --> 00:37:32,057
<i>Do you know my heart?</i>
<i>Will you bless me?</i>

335
00:37:34,402 --> 00:37:39,135
<i>The heaviness keeps growing through</i>
<i>the week it never dissipates...</i>

336
00:37:39,340 --> 00:37:45,904
<i>Will you undress and</i>
<i>wear me like an ornament...</i>

337
00:38:29,990 --> 00:38:37,192
<i>Will l ever disclose my desires?</i>

338
00:38:39,333 --> 00:38:48,765
<i>If you discover my desires</i>
<i>l will acknowledge them with my eyes...</i>

339
00:38:49,009 --> 00:38:54,037
<i>Wherever the lips go..</i>
<i>the heart follows..</i>

340
00:38:54,248 --> 00:38:58,776
<i>Oh dear...l will ask you to rule me...</i>

341
00:38:58,986 --> 00:39:18,430
<i>Tamil knows the parts that</i>
<i>pain and those that don't...</i>

342
00:39:18,773 --> 00:39:27,340
<i>Oh dear...</i>
<i>do you know those parts?</i>

343
00:39:45,966 --> 00:39:49,766
l didn't try to escape hearing
Veera's name, l came with you.

344
00:39:49,970 --> 00:39:52,268
Why are you lamenting? Come.

345
00:39:52,473 --> 00:39:54,873
l'm scared...
Goddess Chotanikkarai Amme!

346
00:40:01,482 --> 00:40:02,278
Come out.

347
00:40:03,150 --> 00:40:06,950
Come out...come.
Stand like a man.

348
00:40:07,988 --> 00:40:10,957
l'm innocent.

349
00:40:11,492 --> 00:40:14,017
l swear l'm not responsible for it.

350
00:40:14,228 --> 00:40:17,129
l'm innocent.
- Tell the truth.

351
00:40:20,067 --> 00:40:21,295
Had a nice journey?

352
00:40:23,604 --> 00:40:24,468
What is this?

353
00:40:26,507 --> 00:40:27,371
Watch?

354
00:40:30,311 --> 00:40:31,335
Presented by me?

355
00:40:35,583 --> 00:40:37,050
l gave you my sister too.

356
00:40:39,520 --> 00:40:40,384
Where is she now?

357
00:40:41,522 --> 00:40:42,511
Where is she?

358
00:40:43,858 --> 00:40:45,416
l don't know.
- Did you lose her?

359
00:40:48,128 --> 00:40:49,925
Answer him.
- But still wearing the watch?

360
00:40:51,198 --> 00:40:54,065
You lost my sister but
keeping the watch safely.

361
00:40:54,268 --> 00:40:56,327
Please don't kill me,
l'm innocent.

362
00:40:56,537 --> 00:40:58,300
Where is my sister?
- Trust me.

363
00:40:58,505 --> 00:40:59,563
Singarasu, tell him to spare me.

364
00:40:59,940 --> 00:41:02,431
Veeraiah, l'm telling truth,
l'm innocent.

365
00:41:16,891 --> 00:41:20,622
All of you give poses like real villains,
the photo must scare them.

366
00:41:21,161 --> 00:41:24,187
Don't act smart,
take a photo quickly.

367
00:41:27,134 --> 00:41:29,227
Will you take a photo
or shall l take your head?

368
00:41:29,436 --> 00:41:31,063
l'll take it.

369
00:41:31,372 --> 00:41:33,602
lf you stand still,
l'll take a photo.

370
00:41:33,974 --> 00:41:36,442
One punch, she'll keep quiet.

371
00:42:14,048 --> 00:42:15,140
lt's a scarecrow.

372
00:42:17,017 --> 00:42:18,712
Even crows will not get scared of it.

373
00:42:19,553 --> 00:42:21,316
Don't take a step further.

374
00:42:37,304 --> 00:42:40,205
Where's the nearest hospital?
- Get the truck here.

375
00:42:40,407 --> 00:42:42,500
l want first aid box,
and pain killers.

376
00:42:45,446 --> 00:42:49,314
Blood is still bleeding, immediate
hospitalisation can save hand.

377
00:42:51,418 --> 00:42:53,181
Leave us for alone
for few minutes.

378
00:43:00,461 --> 00:43:02,622
Aren't you Veera's sister's husband?

379
00:43:02,997 --> 00:43:05,397
He cut my hand, sir.
- Didn't spare brother-in-law too?

380
00:43:06,166 --> 00:43:08,031
He's not a man but beast.

381
00:43:08,235 --> 00:43:09,224
He's a beast.
- ls it?

382
00:43:10,771 --> 00:43:15,037
What's the message by sending
brother-in-law with a hand cut?

383
00:43:17,311 --> 00:43:21,441
l can't bear this pain,
take me to the hospital.

384
00:43:25,219 --> 00:43:28,655
What's he trying to say with
a scarecrow in sari and you behind it?

385
00:43:29,390 --> 00:43:32,188
What is he trying to say?

386
00:43:32,393 --> 00:43:36,193
No...sir...no...

387
00:43:36,397 --> 00:43:37,659
Why did he send you?

388
00:43:38,032 --> 00:43:41,331
lt's paining sir...
- Trying to scare me?

389
00:43:42,603 --> 00:43:44,002
Will he cut my hand too?

390
00:44:05,059 --> 00:44:06,253
Where are you?

391
00:44:07,694 --> 00:44:09,753
lf you don't come quickly,
he'll kill me.

392
00:44:15,469 --> 00:44:18,063
Are you testing your wife's courage?

393
00:44:19,206 --> 00:44:21,071
l'm not brave.

394
00:44:21,742 --> 00:44:23,642
l'm just acting brave.

395
00:44:25,512 --> 00:44:26,604
l'm shouting.

396
00:44:28,115 --> 00:44:29,343
Wearing a mask.

397
00:44:32,119 --> 00:44:35,316
You're here, aren't you?
You didn't go away, did you?

398
00:44:36,190 --> 00:44:37,589
Answer me.

399
00:44:46,600 --> 00:44:47,225
When will you come?

400
00:44:55,742 --> 00:44:58,472
Madam.

401
00:44:59,446 --> 00:45:01,505
How much ever you may cry,
no God will come to save you.

402
00:45:01,715 --> 00:45:03,478
Your husband will also not come.

403
00:45:04,251 --> 00:45:06,378
Rice and onions, have it.

404
00:45:06,720 --> 00:45:08,745
Eat and sleep,
atleast your anger will ease.

405
00:45:09,123 --> 00:45:11,318
You come, she'll eat.

406
00:45:18,765 --> 00:45:19,891
Tape is on, speak.

407
00:45:20,267 --> 00:45:21,700
ls it running?
- Speak.

408
00:45:25,539 --> 00:45:27,769
SP sir, greetings.

409
00:45:28,475 --> 00:45:29,669
Are you fine, sir?

410
00:45:30,644 --> 00:45:32,407
l expect you're not.

411
00:45:32,813 --> 00:45:35,839
We are not fine because
of officers like you.

412
00:45:36,316 --> 00:45:39,615
l'm Veeraiah, a poor man,
illiterate,

413
00:45:39,820 --> 00:45:43,586
not born like you in high society,
but still l'm your enemy.

414
00:45:43,790 --> 00:45:44,848
Villain to you.

415
00:45:45,659 --> 00:45:48,719
Did you see the photo?
Did you recognise her?

416
00:45:50,764 --> 00:45:54,359
l shot the photograph
in day light for you only.

417
00:45:58,272 --> 00:46:00,900
Keep it safely in your purse,
you may not get it again, right?

418
00:46:02,509 --> 00:46:05,205
lf your wife doesn't return,
atleast the photo will be with you.

419
00:46:06,947 --> 00:46:08,471
Why are you getting angry?

420
00:46:11,985 --> 00:46:13,247
ls it paining you now?

421
00:46:13,987 --> 00:46:15,716
ls it hurting your heart severely?

422
00:46:20,994 --> 00:46:27,832
For kidnapping your wife,
you wrecked havoc with men and might.

423
00:46:33,507 --> 00:46:37,170
Your women are diamonds and
our women are just stones, right?

424
00:46:38,779 --> 00:46:41,748
SP sir, pray to God.

425
00:46:42,549 --> 00:46:46,508
That your wife shouldn't face
what my sister had faced.

426
00:46:53,493 --> 00:46:54,687
Be careful with the photo.

427
00:47:20,254 --> 00:47:21,278
lsn't anyone there?

428
00:49:07,761 --> 00:49:08,659
Stop!

429
00:49:10,097 --> 00:49:11,121
Where are you going?

430
00:49:12,432 --> 00:49:15,492
Be a good girl and
sleep silently in one place.

431
00:49:15,802 --> 00:49:16,894
Did you hear me?

432
00:49:35,589 --> 00:49:49,435
<i>Who is this lady in the forest?</i>

433
00:49:50,737 --> 00:50:00,874
<i>Will she give me rain, or</i>
<i>thunder or just magically vanish?</i>

434
00:50:03,150 --> 00:50:07,177
<i>The universe vanished when the girl</i>
<i>with a flower on her head lay down...</i>

435
00:50:11,758 --> 00:50:15,057
<i>The open sky gasps looking at hear face...</i>

436
00:50:17,764 --> 00:50:26,866
<i>lt is thundering outside and</i>
<i>the wet porch is beckoning...</i>

437
00:50:27,073 --> 00:50:32,670
<i>Who is she?</i>

438
00:50:44,191 --> 00:50:49,993
<i>Lost my life on her lips...</i>

439
00:50:53,033 --> 00:50:59,836
<i>Demons inside are hungry</i>
<i>and want you as food...</i>

440
00:51:37,244 --> 00:51:39,212
Let me go!

441
00:52:56,756 --> 00:52:59,224
Rajakka, come up.
- Veera is here.

442
00:53:03,897 --> 00:53:06,058
Move it...move it...

443
00:53:11,771 --> 00:53:13,238
Faster...

444
00:53:20,380 --> 00:53:23,713
lsn't she like our Muthamma
and Guruvamma in this sari?

445
00:53:23,917 --> 00:53:24,576
Yes.

446
00:53:24,784 --> 00:53:28,015
Hey Guruvamma...

447
00:53:30,023 --> 00:53:32,423
Send me back or tie me up.

448
00:53:32,626 --> 00:53:35,823
Walk with us in hot sun for few days,
you'll become dark like us.

449
00:53:37,097 --> 00:53:39,156
Veera, see how angrily
she's looking at you.

450
00:53:40,166 --> 00:53:42,964
Guruvamma! Why don't you
stay back here only?

451
00:53:43,169 --> 00:53:46,400
Why don't you stay with us?

452
00:53:47,240 --> 00:53:48,673
Why are you leaving silently?

453
00:53:48,875 --> 00:53:51,173
Answer me and go.

454
00:53:51,811 --> 00:53:53,176
Will you stay or not?

455
00:53:57,951 --> 00:53:59,179
Where's your gun?

456
00:53:59,786 --> 00:54:02,186
Take it out...shoot me.

457
00:54:04,758 --> 00:54:06,851
That's better than these questions.

458
00:54:08,094 --> 00:54:10,688
Okay, l mustn't ask like this.

459
00:54:11,765 --> 00:54:15,223
SP shouldn't have met you,
he shouldn't have married you,

460
00:54:16,269 --> 00:54:17,702
he shouldn't have come here,

461
00:54:18,071 --> 00:54:19,299
he shouldn't have done
what he did here,

462
00:54:19,673 --> 00:54:20,833
l shouldn't have kidnapped
you in anger,

463
00:54:21,041 --> 00:54:21,939
l shouldn't have thought
of killing you,

464
00:54:22,142 --> 00:54:23,973
you shouldn't have jumped
down from the hill,

465
00:54:24,177 --> 00:54:26,008
l shouldn't have followed you.

466
00:54:26,946 --> 00:54:30,382
When you opened your eyes,
my life shouldn't have come back to me.

467
00:54:32,218 --> 00:54:34,413
Everything has happened,
can't change anything now.

468
00:54:36,356 --> 00:54:39,018
l can't change the path
my heart has taken.

469
00:54:39,225 --> 00:54:41,056
Can't change what l asked you.

470
00:54:42,429 --> 00:54:43,418
Will you stay?

471
00:54:50,103 --> 00:54:51,764
Had you not been married?

472
00:54:52,772 --> 00:54:53,932
Would you've stayed with me?

473
00:55:02,282 --> 00:55:03,271
Forest food?

474
00:55:04,818 --> 00:55:06,080
Rice and tubers?

475
00:55:08,021 --> 00:55:09,488
Can't arrange for feast.

476
00:55:10,924 --> 00:55:13,415
Make with what's available.
lsn't it, Akash?

477
00:55:14,494 --> 00:55:16,189
You can't leave it behind also,

478
00:55:17,030 --> 00:55:21,262
the leftover food may
lead them to us.

479
00:55:23,903 --> 00:55:30,502
But Veeraiah knows
every step we take here.

480
00:55:36,783 --> 00:55:43,154
A forest bird is taking
messages to Veera.

481
00:55:44,758 --> 00:55:47,886
SP is coming, he's coming
towards east with STF.

