few hours of custody.

744
01:27:10,585 --> 01:27:12,883
Madam is with them for 8 days now.
- Stop it l say.

745
01:27:13,421 --> 01:27:14,718
That's what l'm also saying, sir.

746
01:27:14,923 --> 01:27:16,720
Enough sir.
- Take him to base camp.

747
01:27:16,925 --> 01:27:20,224
lf entire battalion goes to forest,
even insects will know.

748
01:27:20,962 --> 01:27:24,557
