They are tough guys,
brainless fellows.

807
01:33:18,620 --> 01:33:22,750
Just say yes, let's cheat them
and escape from here.

808
01:33:22,957 --> 01:33:23,981
Bloody fool!

809
01:33:24,792 --> 01:33:27,590
Don't harm him.
l'm still here only, right?

810
01:33:28,096 --> 01:33:31,156
l'll cut you like a goat,
will you cheat me?

811
01:33:45,813 --> 01:33:50,273
Veera, l can hear funeral band,
l'm hearing sounds that l shouldn't.

812
01:33:50,652 --> 01:33:52,847
l can hear SP's foot sounds,
he's coming.

813
01:33:53,054 --> 01:33:55,215
l'm warning you to be careful.

814
01:33:56,924 --> 01:34:01,361
Yes, l'm SP's man
but l support you.

815
01:34:02,864 --> 01:34:05,628
Did you see them?
Did you see their faces?

816
01:34:06,000 --> 01:34:08,969
They will do anything for you.
They will die for you.

817
01:34:09,671 --> 01:34:10,399
Will you do it?

818
01:34:12,674 --> 01:34:15,074
They must.
Because you gave them life.

819
01:34:16,144 --> 01:34:21,810
l'm asking you only one thing,
why are you taking back their lives?

820
01:34:23,351 --> 01:34:27,310
You're the one to die now.
One more bottle and you'll die.

821
01:34:28,923 --> 01:34:31,653
Send back SP's wife,
stop this fight here.

822
01:34:31,859 --> 01:34:33,156
l'll see all the cases are dropped.

823
01:34:34,195 --> 01:34:35,662
lf l don't send her back.

824
01:34:35,863 --> 01:34:39,264
Keep quiet.
Coming back to square one.

825
01:34:39,701 --> 01:34:40,827
Do you want me to say it?

826
01:34:41,035 --> 01:34:42,935
End of you, total destruction,
annihilation.

827
01:34:43,137 --> 01:34:44,104
Everything will be over.

828
