871
01:37:32,039 --> 01:37:35,839
l'll also go with him.
l'll go with him.

872
01:37:36,043 --> 01:37:39,342
No, you may use bad words
that may not go down well,

873
01:37:40,548 --> 01:37:44,006
brother, l'm not a kid,
l've studied plus 2,

874
01:37:44,485 --> 01:37:46,510
l know all the laws
they speak about.

875
01:37:47,054 --> 01:37:51,457
Just for once, trust and send me.
l'll not spoil your name.

876
01:38:34,702 --> 01:38:39,162
Hey l saw...l saw...
where is sir?

