01:38:40,942 --> 01:38:45,402
l found...went to unreachable
place and met the person.

878
01:38:45,613 --> 01:38:49,913
Give me a medal sir, gold, silver
or bronze, anything will do.

879
01:38:50,117 --> 01:38:50,913
