pray to your God.

919
01:47:54,161 --> 01:47:56,629
Come....come....

920
01:47:57,831 --> 01:48:00,629
No gun, no uniform, no troops.

921
01:48:00,834 --> 01:48:02,461
Got caught alone.

922
01:48:08,275 --> 01:48:09,902
Come...come...

923
01:48:44,044 --> 01:48:50,847
Leave my hand.
