926
01:49:41,301 --> 01:49:47,900
He's Lord Rama and
l'm 10 headed Ravanan, right?

927
01:49:54,948 --> 01:49:56,245
He's alright, isn't he?

928
01:50:09,062 --> 01:50:10,757
l can't beg more than this.

929
01:50:11,965 --> 01:50:12,932
Answer me.

930
01:50:16,637 --> 01:50:17,365
Tell me.

931
01:50:18,972 --> 01:50:19,597
