932
01:50:23,043 --> 01:50:24,271
ls he alive?

933
01:50:31,051 --> 01:50:34,282
Last time l saw him,
he was hale and healthy,

934
01:50:36,990 --> 01:50:40,949
Hanging to the bridge on one hand.

935
01:50:43,830 --> 01:50:47,732
Angry...furious...like a hero.

936
01:50:48,935 --> 01:50:50,027
Hold it tightly.

937
01:50:52,172 --> 01:50:53,639
You may leave it.

938
01:50:54,441 --> 01:50:56,306
Wait, l'll check and tell.

939
01:50:58,211 --> 01:51:04,081
Where are you man?
l'm asking you, right?

940
01:51:08,021 --> 01:51:10,751
You won't believe but he's
crawling up like a snake.

941
01:51:12,959 --> 01:51:14,654
Will you please do me a favour?

942
01:51:14,961 --> 01:51:17,725
Only God grants boons,
l'm a demon.

943
01:51:17,931 --> 01:51:19,159
Don't kill my husband.

944
01:51:19,433 --> 01:51:21,833
lf you come up, only one will survive.

945
01:51:22,035 --> 01:51:23,263
l can leave this rope.

946
01:51:23,470 --> 01:51:26,166
