lf you fire, just ten minutes.

952
01:52:06,913 --> 01:52:09,313
The bad intentions and
thoughts in my heart...

953
01:52:14,488 --> 01:52:16,046
lt'll die along with me.

954
01:52:21,261 --> 01:52:23,456
But if you shoot here,
just a moment,

955
01:52:25,532 --> 01:52:35,237
memories, desires, love, breath,
all will go at a time.

956
01:52:38,779 --> 01:52:39,404
No pain.

957
01:52:43,950 --> 01:52:46,919
