964
01:54:56,182 --> 01:54:58,207
Shouldn't you've taken me
in 14 minutes?

965
01:55:07,260 --> 01:55:08,227
l was scared.

966
01:55:11,932 --> 01:55:17,063
l've come back, Dev.
l'm with you.

967
01:55:25,111 --> 01:55:25,907
Where is he?

968
01:55:29,215 --> 01:55:30,580
